Shine on the bil - low in thy lus-ter mild. Point to the blessed home beyond the skies. Bright star of hope, shine Thou sun and Sav-iour, un - to all ap - pear. on, Bright star of hope shine on, Send out thy light shine on, shine, shine on, and Send out thy light, thy light, in beau-ty bright, Send out thy light, send out thy gladsome light. in beau-ty, beauty bright, Copyright, 1898, by Fillmore Bros.
